  "description_text": "Devilbiss iGo2 Portable Oxygen Concentrator \n\nDevilbiss iGo2 is a Pulse flow based portable Oxygen Concentrator having 5 pulse flow settings with 90% purity. \n\nLightweight and Portable - Devilbiss iGo2 weighs only 2.2kg and is very lightweight to carry around \n\nHighest Operating Altitude - iGo2 has operating altitude of 10,000 feet which is the highest amongst the portable oxygen concentrators \n\nBattery Duration and Recharge time - Devilbiss iGo2 has the battery backup of 3.5 hours at 2 pulse settings and recharge time is 5 hours\n\n5 pulse settings - This portable oxygen concentrator has pulse settings between 1-5\n\nCertifications - Devilbiss iGo2 is FAA, FDA and CE Approved\n\nWarranty - It comes with 2 years of warranty\n\nWhat's in the Box?\n\nDrive DeVilbiss iGo2 Portable Oxygen Concentrator \n\nSingle Battery Pack \n\nCarrying Case \n\nPower Supply (AC/DC Adapter)\n\nAC Power Cord\n\nDC Power Cord (Auto Adapter)\n\nUser Manual",
